OL,6,FGiving evidence on Monday, Motin said
OL,7,Fhe first became aware of the Stena
OL,8,FImmaculate from between 10 and 12
OL,9,Fnautical miles away.
OL,11,FDefence barrister James Leonard KC
OL,12,Fasked: "Did you fall asleep at any
OL,13,Fstage?"
OL,15,FMotin denied this.
OL,17,FMr Leonard asked: "Did you leave the
OL,18,Fbridge to go to the loo, have a
OL,19,Fcomfort break?"
