OL,6,FMotin replied: "I never left the
OL,7,Fbridge at the material time from 8am."
OL,9,FThe defendant told jurors he had two
OL,10,Fvisitors to the bridge that morning,
OL,11,Fthe ship engineer and chief cook, but
OL,12,Fneither was picked up on audio
OL,13,Frecordings.
OL,15,FMr Pernia was engaged in helping the
OL,16,Fchief engineer with some repairs that
OL,17,Fday and was also the designated
OL,18,F"lookout", jurors heard.
