OL,6,FMotin said the crew member was not
OL,7,Frequired as lookout as visibility
OL,8,Fnever dropped to two nautical miles.
OL,10,FMotin has previously told jurors that
OL,11,Fhe had already completed several trips
OL,12,Ffrom Grangemouth in Scotland to
OL,13,FRotterdam in Holland when the tragedy
OL,14,Fstruck.
OL,16,FOnce he became aware of the Stena
OL,17,FImmaculate dead ahead, he delayed
OL,18,Ftaking evasive action because he
OL,19,Fthought it was moving slowly but
OL,20,Funpredictably.
