OL,6,FHe told jurors: "I thought I have no
OL,7,Frudder at all, it's not responding so
OL,8,FI have to look around and see why is
OL,9,Fnot responding."
OL,11,FMotin could see no visual alarms and
OL,12,Fchecked to see that the autopilot
OL,13,Flight was off, the court was told.
OL,15,FHis attempts to change course having
OL,16,Ffailed, Motin recalled a company
OL,17,Frepresentative telling him about a
OL,18,Frudder fault on sister ship, Sanskip
OL,19,FExpress, a few days earlier.
