OL,6,FHe proceeded to stop and restart the
OL,7,Fsteering gear, as he had been advised
OL,8,Fif he experienced a similar problem.
OL,9,FBut, Motin said, "nothing helped".
OL,11,FMr Justice Baker asked: "Did you at
OL,12,Fthe time think about slowing down or
OL,13,Fdid you not give it any thought at
OL,14,Fall?"
OL,16,FMotin replied: "I was thinking that I
OL,17,Fsolve the problem soon instead of
OL,18,Freversing the engine."
